<i>adjective</i>: 확고부동하다 [확꼬부동하다], 굳건하다 [굳껀하다], 견고하다 [견고하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>확고부동하다 [확꼬부동하다]</dt><br>
<dd>firm; solid; determined; unshakable</dd><br>
<dd>확실하고 굳세어 흔들림이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Unshakably confident and firm.</dd><br>
<dt>굳건하다 [굳껀하다]</dt><br>
<dd>firm; unshakable</dd><br>
<dd>굳세고 튼튼하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Strong and solid.</dd><br>
<dt>견고하다 [견고하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. solid; robust</dd><br>
<dd>단단하고 튼튼하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Hard and strong.</dd><br>
<dd>2. firm; unshakable</dd><br>
<dd>흔들림이 없이 굳세고 확고하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Firm and resolute without being shaken.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>